<p>　　break语句退出循环时，它将退出离它最近的那层循环。比如下面的代码，定义一个两维数组，不希望输出第2行。<br /></p><pre t="code" l="cpp">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;<br />int&nbsp;main()<br />{&nbsp;<br />int&nbsp;a[3][3]&nbsp;=&nbsp;{&nbsp;{1,2,3},&nbsp;//第一行<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{4,5,6},&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//第二行<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{7,8,9}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//第三行<br />};<br />for&nbsp;(int&nbsp;i=0;&nbsp;i!=3;&nbsp;++i)&nbsp;{<br />for&nbsp;(int&nbsp;j=0;&nbsp;j!=3;&nbsp;++j)<br />{<br />if&nbsp;(a[i][j]&nbsp;==&nbsp;4)&nbsp;break;&nbsp;//进入第二行时break跳出，只跳出离它最近的for循环<br />printf(&quot;%d\n&quot;,&nbsp;a[i][j]);<br />}<br />}<br />return&nbsp;0;<br />}</pre><p><a href="http://g.hiphotos.baidu.com/zhidao/pic/item/b8389b504fc2d56243975e42e21190ef77c66c86.jpg" target="_blank" title="点击查看大图" class="ikqb_img_alink"><img class="ikqb_img" src="http://g.hiphotos.baidu.com/zhidao/wh%3D600%2C800/sign=7c03768e778b4710ce7af5caf3feefc5/b8389b504fc2d56243975e42e21190ef77c66c86.jpg" esrc="http://g.hiphotos.baidu.com/zhidao/wh%3D450%2C600/sign=0e5e7851c6fdfc03e52debbce10faba2/b8389b504fc2d56243975e42e21190ef77c66c86.jpg" /></a></p>
